title: Me First and the Gimme Gimmes - 1997 - Have a Ball [FLAC]
description:
Have a Ball is the first album by Me First and the Gimme Gimmes. It was released in 1997 on the Fat Wreck Chords independent record label. The album is made up entirely of "Hits of the '60s and '70s".

Track Listing
01 - Danny's Song (Loggins and Messina cover)
02 - Leaving on a Jet Plane (John Denver cover)
03 - Me and Julio Down By the Schoolyard (Paul Simon cover)
04 - One Tin Soldier (Original Caste cover)
05 - Uptown Girl (Billy Joel cover)
06 - I Am a Rock (Simon & Garfunkel cover)
07 - Sweet Caroline (Neil Diamond cover)
08 - Seasons in the Sun (The Kingston Trio cover)
09 - Fire and Rain (James Taylor cover)
10 - Nobody Does It Better (Carly Simon cover)
11 - Mandy (Barry Manilow cover)
12 - Rocket Man (I Think It's Going to Be a Long, Long Time) (Elton John cover)
